的工作。 海底捞被曝给顾客体貌特征打标签！回应称此前已禁止相关备注 _ 海底捞给顾客体貌特征打标签 _ 进行 _ 南都 据其披露的视频画面显示，这些标签包括「20-30 岁，安静，不吃胡萝卜」、「20 多岁瓜子脸嘴巴长得很好看，板栗色头发，大学生，喜欢番茄锅」、「1.68 米左右，戴眼镜，长头发，圆脸型，25 岁左右，喜欢在 App 上投诉」、「吃橙子需要服务员剥」等。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-53cff6ea1db2c052f00943ba120062d2_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "399 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/518288751"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ImMeZ4Y7Kyrx8EAMaCDc3NDU3MTgzINeZ2JAGMBw4zQRACXIJNTE4Mjg4NzUxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1645686500.8037217", "card_id": "Q_518204075", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 364}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "本人 34 岁大龄剩女，想买 130 万房子，但首付缺口 25 万，工资一万左右，有必要买吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "可以借首付，但是亲戚的也是想着早点还的，本来打算要是孤独终老终归有套房，但大家又一直劝我不要这么辛苦。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-086b01a6c3795bfcc9405d9dd3d70944_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "216 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/518204075"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ImMeZ4Y7Kyrx8EAMaCDc3NDM4MzY5IJDG1pAGMD84kAVACnIJNTE4MjA0MDc1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1645686500.8042643", "card_id": "Q_39569160", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "什么是微软式中文？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "（最近看了苹果式中文也想看看微软的）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-7ba3d8d97e582eb2a94fac1cb810320b_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "162 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/39569160"}}, "attached_info": "CjwImMeZ4Y7Kyrx8EAMaBzgwMzQ5ODEg2tzstAUwADh5QAtyCDM5NTY5MTYweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "